      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n* update event insert behavior by @ntawileh in https://github.com/ntawileh/obsidian-google-lookup/pull/63\r\n\r\nYou can choose how to insert event info.  You can either insert the info in-line in the current note (which is the default and the only behavior before this release), or you can now choose to insert the event info in its own note and add a link to that note.  This is similar to the two options of inserting contacts.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/ntawileh/obsidian-google-lookup/compare/1.7.0...1.8.0",
